title: Monsters (2022)
description: The Monster’s blood in his vein exploded when he woke from death! Monsters that existed only in fairy tales appear in the middle of a city in the 21st century, break down buildings and harm humans. A group of humans with extraordinary abilities against them! The story of Naro, an outcast boy who fights against monsters. 妖怪 요괴 Monsters (2022) (Dream Factory Studio)
